description: Fall in love with this delightful 1-bedroom, 1-bath top-floor unit brimming with character and thoughtful details. The open-concept layout features a stylish kitchen complete with white cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The spacious living room includes a cozy corner gas fireplace and opens to a private deck with plenty of sun exposure, perfect for relaxing or entertaining.The oversized bedroom boasts a beautiful bay window and dual closets, while the bathroom offers a luxurious Jacuzzi tub. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, exposed brick, gleaming hardwood floors throughout, and recessed lighting. Bathed in natural sunlight, this inviting home is ideally located just moments from M Street Beach, the Curley Community Center, and the vibrant shops and restaurants of Broadway.
